# Common DevOps Examples

### Monitor application logs

```bash
tail -f application.log
```

### View system logs

```bash
less /var/log/syslog
```

### Count log entries

```bash
wc -l access.log
```

### Compare configuration files

```bash
diff nginx.conf nginx.conf.backup
```

### Search configuration files

```bash
find /etc -name "*.conf"
```

### Find Docker Compose files

```bash
find ~ -name "docker-compose.yml"
```

### Find Git executable

```bash
which git
```

### Find Bash executable and man page

```bash
whereis bash
```

